    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="header">Methods</h2>
            <p>You can programmatically trigger a tab change with our <code class=" language-markup">select_tab</code> method. You have to input the id of the tab you want to switch to. For sample id: <code class=" language-markup">#bas-ui-tab-s3-t1</code></p>

            <pre><code class="language-javascript">
$(document).ready(function(){
    $('#bas-ui-tabs-custom-1').bas_ui_tabs('select_tab', 'bas-ui-tab-s3-t1');
});</code></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="header">Events</h2>

